1
00:00:08,767 --> 00:00:09,881
Murakaza neza nanone

2
00:00:09,881 --> 00:00:12,547
Iki nigice cyakabiri cyijyanye no gukura
 amafaranga muri rubanda

3
00:00:12,547 --> 00:00:16,374
nkuko mubizi, twamaze kuvuga
kubintu byiyamamaza bigendanye no kubona amafaranga

4
00:00:18,179 --> 00:00:20,594
Mucyumweru cyimwe cyangwa bibiri bishize
none ubu tugiye kuvuga ku

5
00:00:20,594 --> 00:00:23,340
bintu byerekeranye
no kubona amafaranga

6
00:00:23,340 --> 00:00:26,123
Cyane rwose, ndetse nka filimi nziza
iba ifite uko ikurikirana

7
00:00:26,123 --> 00:00:27,857
Ubwo rero iki ni igice cya kabiri

8
00:00:27,857 --> 00:00:30,310
Ibijyanye no kubona amafaranga!
cyane rwose!

9
00:00:30,310 --> 00:00:31,749
(Araseka cyane)

10
00:00:31,749 --> 00:00:34,880
Nkuko mubyibuka
mukiganiro cyacu cy'iyamamaza

11
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:38,482
Ibi byo kubona amafaranga ni igihe
ba rwiyemezamirimo

12
00:00:38,482 --> 00:00:42,202
baba bakoresha murandasi

13
00:00:42,202 --> 00:00:45,547
Kubantu babaha amafaranga

14
00:00:45,547 --> 00:00:51,234
Ashobora kubafasha
ndetse no mubikorwa byabo

15
00:00:51,554 --> 00:00:53,726
Yego, rero iyo utekereje kuri ibingibi

16
00:00:53,726 --> 00:00:57,277
Ushobora gubitekerezaho
muri ubu buryo

17
00:00:57,756 --> 00:01:00,721
Ufite kurundi ruhande
rwiyemezamirimo

18
00:01:00,721 --> 00:01:05,024
Kurundi ruhande, uwagufasha
noneho ukaba watanga amakuru y'umushinga

19
00:01:05,024 --> 00:01:07,411
Ibihembo byiza biganisha kubona amafaranga

20
00:01:07,666 --> 00:01:10,075
Uwagufasha ashobora kuguha
amafaranga

21
00:01:10,075 --> 00:01:12,438
Nibindi bintu bitari amafaranga
nko kumenyekana, nibindi

22
00:01:12,438 --> 00:01:14,790
Twavuze kuribyo
mugice cy'iyamamaza

23
00:01:14,790 --> 00:01:17,199
Ariko bifashwa nurubuga

24
00:01:17,199 --> 00:01:19,776
Kandi niyo mpamvu tubibona
nkuburyo bwiza

25
00:01:19,776 --> 00:01:22,762
Ariko uburyo bufatwa
nkubusanzwe

26
00:01:22,762 --> 00:01:27,642
Mumyaka micye yashize, kandi
ni ingenzi kuri ba rwiyemezamirimo

27
00:01:27,642 --> 00:01:32,262
Muburyo bwose bw'ubuyobozi
nibice by'isi

28
00:01:32,496 --> 00:01:35,367
(Kirisitiya) rero, ntabwo bitangaje ko
ibonwa ry'amafaranga

29
00:01:35,367 --> 00:01:39,851
Ryatanze amafaranga menshi
mumyaka itanu ishize

30
00:01:40,641 --> 00:01:45,427
Muri 2012, byari biliyoni 2.7
muri 2013, byari biliyoni 5.1

31
00:01:45,427 --> 00:01:48,305
Abantu barateganyaga ntago
bari babarira ibya 2014

32
00:01:48,305 --> 00:01:50,408
Ariko bijya gukuba kabiri ibyongibyo

33
00:01:50,408 --> 00:01:54,498
Rero mukuri, ni uburyo bwingenzi ubungubu

34
00:01:54,498 --> 00:01:56,263
Kwizi hose

35
00:01:56,263 --> 00:02:00,280
(Kirisitiya) Ubu, abo bakinnyi,
birumvikana, bafite akamaro kabo

36
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:02,835
Nkuko twabivuzeho gato
mugice cy'iyamamaza

37
00:02:03,955 --> 00:02:06,666
Akamaro kabo kagenda gahinduka

38
00:02:06,666 --> 00:02:09,446
Rimwe na Rimwe ba rwiyemezamirimo
batanga amafaranga

39
00:02:09,446 --> 00:02:12,034
Ariko muri rusange , niba rwiyemezamirimo

40
00:02:12,034 --> 00:02:13,982
Ni abantu bakunda gukora ibintu

41
00:02:13,982 --> 00:02:16,539
Hari abahanzi, abafana
hari nakandi kamaro

42
00:02:16,539 --> 00:02:20,654
Abantu bafata kamwe
bakakira amafaranga kubandi

43
00:02:20,654 --> 00:02:26,758
Kandi mvuze muri rusange, fata igice
muri uku gushaka amafaranga

44
00:02:26,838 --> 00:02:29,884
(Mariko) abantu bamwe baba banashaka
gutakaza igihe mu ibonwa ryamafaranga

45
00:02:29,884 --> 00:02:32,728
Kuberako bishimishije kubibona
noneho bakaba abari aho batanga amafaranga

46
00:02:32,728 --> 00:02:36,108
Kuberako bishimishije gufasha abandi
bafite gahunda zisobantuse

47
00:02:36,108 --> 00:02:38,531
(Kirisitiya) rero dutekereze
 kunzira zitandukanye

48
00:02:38,531 --> 00:02:41,888
Ushobora kubonamo amafaranga
uyashakishije kuri interineti

49
00:02:41,888 --> 00:02:45,689
Kandi twagaragaje
 butanu cyangwa butandatu hano

50
00:02:46,299 --> 00:02:48,362
Bikoresha inzira zitandukanye

51
00:02:48,362 --> 00:02:50,095
Kandi kuruhande rwibumoso rwizi paji

52
00:02:50,095 --> 00:02:55,800
Ibyo twakoze nukubereka ingero
zimbuga zibonekaho abafasha

53
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:59,161
Ziri hanze aha
zikoresha uburyo butandukanye

54
00:02:59,161 --> 00:03:03,254
Icyambere cyaba kuyabonera
mumitungo yabantu

55
00:03:03,254 --> 00:03:06,461
Kandi kuri ubu buryo, icyo ibi bisobanuye
nuko urimo uratanga

56
00:03:06,461 --> 00:03:07,711
Igice cya kompanyi yawe

57
00:03:07,711 --> 00:03:10,084
Nkuko twabivuzeho
icyi cyumweru cyashize

58
00:03:11,004 --> 00:03:14,555
Ntago ari ibintu biri mubihugu byinshi
kwisi muri iyi minsi

59
00:03:14,843 --> 00:03:18,316
Ndatekereza ubwongereza,
ositarariya, n'ubutaliyani

60
00:03:18,316 --> 00:03:22,180
Ni ingero zahantu
aho byamaze kwemerwa n'amategeko

61
00:03:22,180 --> 00:03:25,284
Ndetse na amerika irimo iregera
iyo nziira ubungubu

62
00:03:25,824 --> 00:03:30,514
Ikibazo nuko iyo ufite
abantu benshi bagufasha

63
00:03:30,514 --> 00:03:34,943
utekereza kugira
muri kompanyi

64
00:03:34,943 --> 00:03:36,885
Ufite kugira
amategeko runaka

65
00:03:36,885 --> 00:03:40,401
Iyo ari amafaranga makeya
(yiruhutsa), nibindi

66
00:03:40,401 --> 00:03:43,201
None ubwo ntago ufatwa
Nikibazo gikomeye

67
00:03:43,201 --> 00:03:48,268
(Kirisitiya) ni ikibazo gikomeye
ubwo rero ubu buryo bwo kubona amafaranga nuburyo bumwe

68
00:03:48,268 --> 00:03:50,393
Mvuze muri rusange,
ntago ariyo nzira imenyerewe

69
00:03:50,393 --> 00:03:52,797
Ariko ni ikintu ubona
kiraho kandi cyiza

70
00:03:52,797 --> 00:03:55,935
(Kirisitiya) nikintu cyiza, mubyukuri
kandi ibihugu byinshi birabikora ubu

71
00:03:56,296 --> 00:03:59,050
Ubundi buryo bwo kubona
 amafaranga nkumwenda

72
00:03:59,050 --> 00:04:06,209
Kandi ubu buryo,
bugiye kukuzanira inguzanyo

73
00:04:06,209 --> 00:04:08,085
Kandi ugomba kubishyura ayo wahawe

74
00:04:08,085 --> 00:04:10,378
(Mariko) Kandi harimo inyungu wakwishyura
uzasanga ari nyinshi

75
00:04:10,378 --> 00:04:12,622
Kurusha inyungu
wabona mu mabanki

76
00:04:12,622 --> 00:04:16,952
(Kirisitiya) Yego, ubusanzwe
inguzanyo ifite inyungu nkeya cyangwa ntayo

77
00:04:16,952 --> 00:04:20,131
Ugendeye kurubuga
ariko buri kimwe kiratandukanye

78
00:04:20,131 --> 00:04:21,595
Kandi ni kimwe muburyo bushoboka

79
00:04:21,595 --> 00:04:25,295
Nanone, ni kimwe mubimenyerewe
mukubona amafaranga

80
00:04:25,295 --> 00:04:27,316
Ariko ni ikintu ugomba kumenya

81
00:04:27,316 --> 00:04:31,338
Mugihe ushoboye
kubona ayo mafaranga

82
00:04:31,338 --> 00:04:35,596
Ubwoko bwa gatatu bwitwa
ubushingiye kubihembo

83
00:04:35,596 --> 00:04:42,290
Kandi aho niho utanga ubufasha
ubundi ukabona ibihembo nyuma

84
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,169
Kukuba waratanze ubufasha

85
00:04:44,169 --> 00:04:45,679
(Mariko) twazanye ingero

86
00:04:45,679 --> 00:04:48,631
Yego, iki ni ikintu
umwungiriza wacu, Netra yakoze

87
00:04:48,631 --> 00:04:50,535
Yaragiye
kuri uru rubuga rwo kubona amafaranga

88
00:04:50,535 --> 00:04:52,322
Nkuko mwabibona kuri iyi paji

89
00:04:52,322 --> 00:04:56,653
Mukumenyekana
kubera gutanga inkunga

90
00:04:56,653 --> 00:05:00,296
Ibyo yari ashoboye gukora
ni uko yafashe ifoto yumuhanzi

91
00:05:00,296 --> 00:05:03,769
Noneho afata agace kumwenda
kazakoreshwa

92
00:05:03,769 --> 00:05:08,024
Hanyuma
yatanze ubufasha noneho abona

93
00:05:08,024 --> 00:05:15,100
Abona akakantu nkigihembo
kubera kuba yaratanze iyi mfashanyo

94
00:05:16,674 --> 00:05:21,432
Ubundi buryo nimbere yo kugurisha

95
00:05:21,432 --> 00:05:23,389
Kandi twavuzeho gato
kuri icyi mukwamamaza

96
00:05:23,389 --> 00:05:29,434
Aha niho uba ufite uko igicuruzwa kizaba gisa
cyangwa utaratangira kugikora

97
00:05:29,434 --> 00:05:33,099
Ariko urimo uragurisha
ibyo ufite mbere

98
00:05:33,099 --> 00:05:39,431
Ubu nuburyo bwiza bwo kugera ku isoko
ukanabona amafaranga

99
00:05:39,431 --> 00:05:43,570
Yo gukora ibicuruzwa
cyangwa kwaguka kumushinga wawe

100
00:05:43,970 --> 00:05:45,422
Ibyo nibyambere yo kugurisha

101
00:05:45,422 --> 00:05:50,564
Ubungubu, kubyo gucuruza,
 hari imbuga nka Tilt zubaka

102
00:05:50,564 --> 00:05:52,779
Kuburyo iyo ugeze nkuntego

103
00:05:52,779 --> 00:05:56,892
Ushobora gukomeza kugurisha
nkuburyo bw'inyongera bwo kugurisha

104
00:05:56,892 --> 00:06:00,994
Nkigurisha kuri interineti
ibicuruzwa byawe kumbuga

105
00:06:00,994 --> 00:06:02,658
Iyo umaze kugera kuntego yawe

106
00:06:02,658 --> 00:06:05,456
Noneho iyo washyizeho ibintu
wamaze kubona ibyambere y'ubucuruzi

107
00:06:05,456 --> 00:06:10,794
Noneho iyo ugeze kuntego,
 ukomeza kugurisha muri ubwo buryo

108
00:06:10,794 --> 00:06:13,194
(Mariko) usanga ari
igisubizo cyiza

109
00:06:13,194 --> 00:06:15,300
Kuberako ushobora gusigara
kuburyo bumwe

110
00:06:15,300 --> 00:06:16,702
Abantu bazi kuri kuri ubwo buryo

111
00:06:16,702 --> 00:06:19,850
Ubwo kuva mubyambere yo kugurisha
ukagurisha byinshi

112
00:06:19,850 --> 00:06:21,627
Kandi usanga nabyo ari byiza kuri ubu buryo

113
00:06:21,627 --> 00:06:25,066
Kuberako bafata amakompanyi
iyo zirimo zikora

114
00:06:25,066 --> 00:06:27,814
Rero ndatekereza ko ari
uburyo bwo gutsinda kumpande zombi

115
00:06:28,060 --> 00:06:32,851
Uburyo bwa nyuma
turimo turita gukusanya

116
00:06:32,851 --> 00:06:35,693
Aho niho umuntu ashobora kuvuga ati

117
00:06:35,693 --> 00:06:38,493
Nzagupangira uko uzamamaza

118
00:06:38,493 --> 00:06:41,466
Cyangwa nzagufasha mukwamamaza

119
00:06:41,466 --> 00:06:43,776
Mbese, abantu bakaguha igihe cyabo

120
00:06:43,776 --> 00:06:46,161
Kandi aha niho, ni uyu murongo usekeje

121
00:06:46,161 --> 00:06:48,835
Hagati yo kubona amafaranga
naho uyakura

122
00:06:48,835 --> 00:06:53,166
Kuberako aho uyakura ni
 ukugerageza gusaba amafaranga

123
00:06:53,166 --> 00:06:57,342
Cyangwa ubwenge mubantu
kuri interineti, kwisi hose

124
00:06:57,342 --> 00:06:59,600
Kandi ibi binabika amafaranga

125
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:03,027
Kuberako  ubu ntago ufite kwishyura umuntu
ngo agutegurire uko uzamamaza

126
00:07:03,027 --> 00:07:07,399
(Mariko)Cyane, kandi byagufasha
kumenya ibindi bintu

127
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:09,870
Wakoresha ngo ubone amafaranga
kuberako ntamuntu uri hanze aha

128
00:07:09,870 --> 00:07:12,893
wagufasha
mubikorwa byawe

129
00:07:12,893 --> 00:07:15,322
cyangwa mubintu uzakoresha
urimo ushaka

130
00:07:15,322 --> 00:07:18,333
Rero wabonye izi ngero
ariko ushobora gukomeza kwibaza

131
00:07:18,333 --> 00:07:20,895
Kuki nkeneye gushaka amafaranga
muri ubu buryo kuki nabikora?

132
00:07:20,895 --> 00:07:22,910
Ibigize iyamamaza ni ikintu kimwe

133
00:07:22,910 --> 00:07:25,021
Ariko ibijyanye namafaranga
ni ikindi cyintu

134
00:07:25,021 --> 00:07:28,967
Yego, ndatekereza ko ari uburyo
bwiza bwo gutangira kubona amafaranga

135
00:07:29,347 --> 00:07:33,221
Kugera ku madolari menshi

136
00:07:34,231 --> 00:07:37,600
Kandi  uretse kuruhande rumwe
twamaze kuvugaho

137
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:40,455
Aho ukura amafaranga mumitungo yabandi

138
00:07:40,455 --> 00:07:43,901
Mubihe byinshi abafasha abandi
ntago bafata imitungo mumushinga

139
00:07:43,901 --> 00:07:47,293
Yego, kandi ugomba kwibuka ko utegetswe

140
00:07:47,293 --> 00:07:51,049
gukoresha ibyo
ubona muri ayo mafaranga

141
00:07:52,029 --> 00:07:54,013
Ugendeye kuntego wagaragaje

142
00:07:54,013 --> 00:07:57,434
Rero ni ukugumana isezerano
kuri ibyo bintu

143
00:07:57,434 --> 00:08:00,053
ko uzabishyira mubikorwa
kandi ugasezeranya kubikora

144
00:08:00,053 --> 00:08:01,314
Kandi iyo utabikoze, birumvikana

145
00:08:01,314 --> 00:08:05,352
bishobora gutuma
umenyekana nabi nawe

146
00:08:05,352 --> 00:08:08,172
Rero birakenewe
rimwe na rimwe ni itegeko

147
00:08:08,172 --> 00:08:10,738
Kandi mubintu byinshi urashaka
 kubikora uko ubonye

148
00:08:11,068 --> 00:08:13,335
Noneho reka tuvuge
uburyo bwo kubona amafaranga

149
00:08:13,335 --> 00:08:16,962
Dukeneye kubona itandukaniro
 hagati y'uburyo bubiri

150
00:08:16,962 --> 00:08:20,698
kandi bishobora no kugira ingaruka kuburyo
wubaka uko ubona amafaranga

151
00:08:20,698 --> 00:08:23,927
Icyambere ni ikidahinduka
 kandi usanga aribyose cyangwa ntacyo

152
00:08:23,927 --> 00:08:25,992
Mukuri, iyo utageze kubyo wiyemeje

153
00:08:25,992 --> 00:08:28,594
ntugire amafaranga ubona
noneho icyindi ni uguhinduka

154
00:08:28,594 --> 00:08:30,696
Ariho ubona uko
 ugumana ayo wabonye yose

155
00:08:30,696 --> 00:08:32,571
Utitaye kuntego ufite

156
00:08:32,571 --> 00:08:35,538
Tuzavuga kubyiza
 nibibi byaburikimwe kubizakurikira

157
00:08:35,942 --> 00:08:38,393
(Mariko) Kubijyanye no kubona amafaranga bidahinduka
ibyabyose cyangwa byantabyo

158
00:08:38,393 --> 00:08:40,487
Ibyiza biragaragara

159
00:08:40,487 --> 00:08:42,509
Ufite amadolari ushaka kugeraho

160
00:08:42,509 --> 00:08:45,623
Bigaragarira buriwese
kuri wowe no kubandi

161
00:08:45,623 --> 00:08:49,764
Bizana kumva  ushaka kubyihutisha
kandi bizana ishyaka

162
00:08:49,764 --> 00:08:52,048
Cyane cyane iyo urimo kubona
wegera ayo mafaranga

163
00:08:52,048 --> 00:08:53,648
Abantu bashoboye kuvuga
nzafasha uyu muntu

164
00:08:53,648 --> 00:08:56,168
Numvise mubabariye
ariko ntago yabigeraho

165
00:08:56,168 --> 00:08:59,464
Rero ubu ndumva mfite ishyaka ryo kumufasha

166
00:08:59,464 --> 00:09:00,898
(Kirisitiya) uhamagara inshuti zawe
ukavuga

167
00:09:00,898 --> 00:09:02,898
(Mariko) nkeneye( aseka)

168
00:09:02,898 --> 00:09:05,785
Birajya kuri babantu bafasha
kandi byubaka icyizere

169
00:09:05,785 --> 00:09:09,150
Kuberako uravuga uti ndabikora
ndagera kuri aya mafaranga

170
00:09:10,850 --> 00:09:14,238
Nimuburyo bwo kuvugana nabandi
ko nutagera kuri ayo mafaranga

171
00:09:14,238 --> 00:09:16,366
Ntacyo bimaze gutangira umushinga rero

172
00:09:16,366 --> 00:09:19,290
Rero bigaragaza ko
wabitekerejeho cyane

173
00:09:19,290 --> 00:09:23,498
Ubu buryo butangwa kur  hafi y'ubwoko bwose
bwo kubona amafaranga hanze aha

174
00:09:23,828 --> 00:09:26,048
(Kirisitiya) muburyo bwingarukambi hano

175
00:09:26,048 --> 00:09:29,370
Iyo utageze kuntego yawe
ubona ubusa

176
00:09:29,370 --> 00:09:32,733
Muri rusange, hariya hashobora kubaho uburyo runaka
kumbuga zimwe na zimwe zituma wishyura

177
00:09:32,733 --> 00:09:36,505
Amafaranga menshi ukabona icyo ufite
aho kugera kuntego yawe

178
00:09:36,505 --> 00:09:38,738
Ariko muri rusange, ntugire icyo ubona

179
00:09:38,738 --> 00:09:42,998
Rero hari inkeke hano

180
00:09:42,998 --> 00:09:46,495
Hari ninkeke
yo kuzana icyintu gihanze

181
00:09:46,915 --> 00:09:49,473
Kuberako urashaka gukurura abazagufasha

182
00:09:49,473 --> 00:09:51,610
Kandi ukeneye ko baguha amafaranga

183
00:09:51,610 --> 00:09:53,734
Cyangwa ntugere
kuntego yawe

184
00:09:54,484 --> 00:09:56,914
Bwanyuma, ibi bisaba icyizere cyinshi

185
00:09:56,914 --> 00:10:00,695
Ugomba kumva ko
ugiye kubona ayo mafaranga

186
00:10:00,695 --> 00:10:03,067
 Ugomba gutekereza
kucyo ushaka kugeraho

187
00:10:03,067 --> 00:10:07,090
Ko wumva ushaka
kubona ayo mafaranga yose

188
00:10:07,090 --> 00:10:11,139
Ubu, ubusanzwe, iyo ubonye menshi kuri ayo

189
00:10:11,969 --> 00:10:14,923
Noneho ukagumana icyiricyo cyose
cyiri hejuru yayo washakaga

190
00:10:14,923 --> 00:10:19,853
Reka tuvuge kungero runaka
kubidahinduka

