193
00:10:30,754 --> 00:10:34,563
Biza kurangira bagize 33,000 byamadolari

194
00:10:34,873 --> 00:10:38,244
Noneho icyakabiri cyari iyi saha

195
00:10:38,824 --> 00:10:43,259
Yari izavamo 60,000 by'amadolari
cyangwa icyintu nkicyo

196
00:10:43,259 --> 00:10:45,837
Birangira babonye 372,000 by'amadolari

197
00:10:45,837 --> 00:10:49,259
Kandi ibi byabaye kuri uru
 rubuga rwa Indigogo

198
00:10:51,009 --> 00:10:53,500
Byiswe uburyo bwo gusaba

199
00:10:53,500 --> 00:10:55,514
Usanga, nkuko twabigaragaje mbere

200
00:10:55,514 --> 00:11:00,060
Bigufasha gukomeza ugurisha
 ukoresheje ubwo buryo

201
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:03,560
kuberako warenze
intego namafaranga runaka

202
00:11:04,506 --> 00:11:06,823
(Mariko) reka tujye kuburyo
bwo kubona amafaranga  buhinduka noneho

203
00:11:06,823 --> 00:11:09,638
kandi nanone hari ibyiza
n'ibibi byibingibi

204
00:11:09,638 --> 00:11:12,435
(Mariko) Ndaza kuvuga kubyiza
(Kirisitiya) nanjye ndumuntu wibibi!

205
00:11:12,435 --> 00:11:14,324
(Mariko) Uravuga kubibi, sawa

206
00:11:14,324 --> 00:11:17,149
Ibyiza nanone birigaragaza

207
00:11:17,149 --> 00:11:21,685
Nukuberako udafite icyo cyintu
cyidahinduka ushaka kugeraho

208
00:11:22,725 --> 00:11:25,598
Iki ntago ari icyintu kingenzi
kugishyiraho

209
00:11:25,598 --> 00:11:29,628
Ushobora gushyiraho intego imwe 
cyangwa iyindi ariko ni ingenzi kuyigeraho

210
00:11:29,628 --> 00:11:33,341
Rero ntago ari ingenzi
nko kugendera kuri gahunda

211
00:11:33,341 --> 00:11:36,430
Ntago ugomba kugira impungenge
kukugera kuntego yawe y'amafaranga

212
00:11:36,430 --> 00:11:38,947
Kandi ntaninkeke y'igihe uba ufite
kuri icyo gikorwa

213
00:11:38,947 --> 00:11:40,379
KUrundi ruhande hari ibibi

214
00:11:40,379 --> 00:11:43,183
(Kirisitiya) Yego, hari bicye 
byo kwizeza abaguha amafaranga

215
00:11:43,183 --> 00:11:48,193
Ntago ari ibintu bisanzwe ko icyi
 cyintu cyose cyizakurwaho mugihe runaka

216
00:11:48,193 --> 00:11:51,325
Kandi ndatekereza abantu benshi bafasha
ntago bizera

217
00:11:51,325 --> 00:11:54,706
Kuba ugerageza gukora icyintu
nkicyidahinduka

218
00:11:54,706 --> 00:11:56,839
Kandi hashobora kuba imbaraga mukubona
amafaranga menshi

219
00:11:56,839 --> 00:12:00,949
Kuberako gahunda runaka zaguca 
amafaranga make

220
00:12:00,949 --> 00:12:04,151
Cyangwa niba utageze kuntego yawe
bizagusaba kwishyura menshi, nibindi

221
00:12:04,151 --> 00:12:07,680
Ukomeza kuyabona, ariko ugomba kwishyura
amafaranga menshi

222
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:11,481
Kandi ntago ari burigihe bitangwa
kuri buri gahunda

223
00:12:11,481 --> 00:12:18,771
Ubusanzwe, ntago ufite amahirwe 
kugukora burigihe ibihinduka

224
00:12:19,339 --> 00:12:23,208
Hano hari urugero rwiza rw'ibihinduka

225
00:12:23,208 --> 00:12:30,102
Icyi cyari ububiko bw'ubuki
noneho abo bantu bakigira utubiko tubiri

226
00:12:30,102 --> 00:12:33,187
Buzatanga
ubuki kuriwowe ako kanya

227
00:12:33,187 --> 00:12:35,687
Kuburyo utari ukeneye kwinjiramo

228
00:12:35,687 --> 00:12:37,506
(Mariko) uburyo bwizewe

229
00:12:37,506 --> 00:12:42,006
(Kirisitiya) hano urabona ko babonye
miliyoni 8.5 by'amadolari

230
00:12:42,006 --> 00:12:43,443
Kandi barimo kugurisha ibyo bintu

231
00:12:43,443 --> 00:12:45,961
Kumadolari 600 wabona icyo ubikamo ubuki

232
00:12:45,961 --> 00:12:48,662
Kandi bari bitonze kumenya niba
inzuki zitarimo

233
00:12:48,662 --> 00:12:49,756
(Araseka cyane)

234
00:12:49,756 --> 00:12:52,240
(Mariko) ariko icyintu gishimishije ni uko
iyo witegereje wegereye

235
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:56,900
Nuko bari bafite intego yamadolari 70,000
rero byari bitangaje aribyiza

236
00:12:56,900 --> 00:13:02,196
Urimo urasaba 70,000 by'amadolari
noneho ukabona miliyoni 8.5

237
00:13:02,196 --> 00:13:05,448
Ubu nubwikube butangaje

238
00:13:05,448 --> 00:13:11,533
Yego, icyo ushaka gukora ni ugufata 
umwanzuro ubuhe buryo ushaka kubaho

239
00:13:11,533 --> 00:13:13,611
Kandi hari ibinini hano hanze

240
00:13:13,611 --> 00:13:16,399
Ariko hari 
nudutoya twinshi natwo

241
00:13:16,399 --> 00:13:19,127
Rero hari uburyo bwinshi bwo kubona
 amafaranga bugutegereje

242
00:13:20,027 --> 00:13:24,464
Ikibazo kimwe kingenzi ni, ninde ushaka
guhatana nawe kumafaranga?

243
00:13:24,464 --> 00:13:27,229
Kuberako niba hari miliyoni 5
indi mishinga hanze aha

244
00:13:27,229 --> 00:13:29,056
Uri umwe muri miliyoni 5

245
00:13:29,056 --> 00:13:32,278
Ndetse izo mbuga zagira abantu 
bacye bahatanira ayo mafaranga

246
00:13:32,278 --> 00:13:36,585
Kandi ibyo byasobanura  kubona
kumvwa kumushinga wawe

247
00:13:36,585 --> 00:13:40,526
Nanone zimwe 
muri izo gahunda zirihariye

248
00:13:40,526 --> 00:13:42,989
Bagomba kugira
uko bangana

249
00:13:42,989 --> 00:13:47,697
Intego runaka, hashobora kuba
abatanga amafaranga batandukanye

250
00:13:47,697 --> 00:13:50,342
Bajyanye nimbuga zitandukanye

251
00:13:50,342 --> 00:13:53,452
Rero ni ingenzi
kunyura muri ibyo bintu

252
00:13:53,452 --> 00:13:56,989
Noneho ufate umwanzuro kukiza kuri wowe
nuruhe rubuga urimo gushaka

253
00:13:56,989 --> 00:14:00,740
Cyane cyane ikibazo cy'ubwoko
bwabazagufasha ushaka gukurura

254
00:14:00,740 --> 00:14:04,428
Abazagufasha bamwe bashobora kuba
bari kumbuga runaka batari kuzindi

255
00:14:04,428 --> 00:14:06,703
Rero iki ni
 ikibazo kingenzi gushakira umuti

256
00:14:06,703 --> 00:14:09,095
Nkurugero, bakagombye kugira
abakiriya

257
00:14:09,095 --> 00:14:10,936
bagura ibicuruzwa byawe kuru urwo rubuga

258
00:14:10,936 --> 00:14:13,892
Ndetse nabantu bashaka
kugufasha kurundi rubuga

259
00:14:13,892 --> 00:14:17,277
Niba urimo ugerageza kugurisha
kubantu bashaka kugufasha

260
00:14:17,277 --> 00:14:21,790
Ntago ubwo bwaba ari uburyo bwiza
kuri rubanda ufite hariya

261
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:24,347
Ubungubu, ahantu hashobora kuba 
hanini cyangwa hato

262
00:14:24,347 --> 00:14:28,215
Icyo ufite gutekerezaho
ni uburyo abo ubwira ari benshi

263
00:14:28,215 --> 00:14:30,327
Nibande bingenzi ushaka kugeraho?

264
00:14:30,327 --> 00:14:32,286
Ndetse nurubuga rwiza kuri wowe?

265
00:14:32,286 --> 00:14:34,209
Kuguha ubumenyi
kucyo ibi bisobanuye

266
00:14:34,209 --> 00:14:36,614
Twaguhaye ingero nkeya hano

267
00:14:37,164 --> 00:14:39,744
Nkurugero, kwibanda kuhantu

268
00:14:39,744 --> 00:14:41,922
Hari iyitwa cheetah fund

269
00:14:41,922 --> 00:14:44,588
Itakira abasaba bashashya ubu

270
00:14:44,588 --> 00:14:47,260
Ariko mbere iyo wabaga muri afurika
ufite igitekerezo cyiza

271
00:14:47,260 --> 00:14:49,526
Hanyuma ufite intego, bari
kukuzira

272
00:14:49,526 --> 00:14:51,807
Bagahuza nawe

273
00:14:51,807 --> 00:14:53,412
(Mariko) hano hari urundi

274
00:14:53,412 --> 00:14:55,181
Uru rundi rugero ni carrotmob, 
nkurugero

275
00:14:55,181 --> 00:14:58,234
Igitekerezo gishimishije hano

276
00:14:58,234 --> 00:15:03,440
Ushobora gukora itsinda ryabantu
ryafasha rwiyemezamirimo

277
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:06,749
Rero iyo ufite hoteli ntoya
kandi ukeneye kugira amafaranga

278
00:15:06,749 --> 00:15:09,479
Yo kuvugurura hoteli
ukeneye abantu baguma muri hoteli

279
00:15:09,479 --> 00:15:11,189
Kugirango ubone inyungu nyinshi

280
00:15:11,189 --> 00:15:15,448
Umuntu runaka, wagufasha, ashobora gushyira kumurongo
abacuti be bose bakaguma muri hoteli yawe

281
00:15:15,784 --> 00:15:18,850
Kandi ibyo bizaguha amafaranga
ukeneye ngo uvugurure

282
00:15:18,850 --> 00:15:21,177
(Mariko) rero ufite kumenya neza
ko barimo bagira ibihe byiza

283
00:15:21,177 --> 00:15:22,175
(Araseka cyane)

284
00:15:22,175 --> 00:15:23,905
(Kirisitiya) ibyo nibyo

285
00:15:23,905 --> 00:15:26,056
Rero, gutekereza kugiye kugufasha uwo ariwe

286
00:15:26,056 --> 00:15:31,717
Ni inama
gutekereza kuri icyi cyintu

287
00:15:32,137 --> 00:15:35,529
Ni abahe bantu
ushaka gukurura ngo babe abazagufasha?

288
00:15:35,529 --> 00:15:38,140
Hanyuma rero, kugerageza guhuza ibyo 
nabazagufasha

289
00:15:38,140 --> 00:15:40,835
Bajyanye
nimbuga zitandukanye

290
00:15:41,875 --> 00:15:47,782
Hano imyaka, igitsina, inyungu
twamaze kugaragaza ahantu

291
00:15:48,072 --> 00:15:52,147
Ibyo imbuga zishimishwa nabyo

292
00:15:52,387 --> 00:15:54,770
Ibyo bashaka gukora kuri uru rubuga

293
00:15:54,770 --> 00:15:56,789
Ese abantu batanga amafaranga
bashaka igice cya kompanyi yawe

294
00:15:56,789 --> 00:15:58,999
cyangwa bashaka kugira icyo
 babona hacyiri kare?

295
00:15:58,999 --> 00:16:01,229
Ese barashaka
kureba uko igicuruzwa cyizaba kimeze?

296
00:16:01,229 --> 00:16:05,277
Cyangwa bamere neza bo ubwabo?
Yego, abantu bamwe bakunda gufasha

297
00:16:05,277 --> 00:16:08,349
(Mariko) ni icyintu 
kiza nka kirisitiya, burigihe ashaka gufasha abantu

298
00:16:08,349 --> 00:16:09,635
(Araseka cyane)

299
00:16:09,635 --> 00:16:12,166
(Kirisitiya) nibyo
burigihe mfasha abantu

300
00:16:13,096 --> 00:16:16,213
(Mariko) abantu bafasha ni igice kimwe
cyo gushaka igisubizo

301
00:16:16,213 --> 00:16:21,352
Ariko icyindi gice cyicyo gikorwa
ni ibintu bikurura abantu bagufasha

302
00:16:21,352 --> 00:16:23,626
Kurubuga rwawe noneho ukabona
abazagufasha mumafaranga

303
00:16:23,626 --> 00:16:27,235
Ni ikintu kimwe kubona abantu bafite ishyaka
ariko icyindi kintu ni ukubona abantu bafite gahunda

304
00:16:27,235 --> 00:16:29,510
Kandi hari ubushakashatsi bugaragaza

305
00:16:29,510 --> 00:16:33,933
Ibintu bituma
ubona aba bantu bagufasha

306
00:16:33,933 --> 00:16:36,335
Kandi hari ibintu bibiri byingenzi

307
00:16:36,335 --> 00:16:39,405
Icyambere ni ukwizerwa
ikindi ni ugukurura abantu

308
00:16:39,405 --> 00:16:42,455
Rero muburyo bwo kwizerwa,
nibijyanye ni ubunyamwuga

309
00:16:43,075 --> 00:16:46,194
Ndetse nuburyo umushinga wawe wacamo
 bifite akamaro cyane

310
00:16:46,194 --> 00:16:50,538
Kandi gukurura abantu ni
icyintu kingenzi, igicuruzwa cyingenzi

311
00:16:50,538 --> 00:16:53,324
Cyangwa icyintu runaka
urimo ushaka gukemura

312
00:16:53,324 --> 00:16:57,045
Kandi uburyo wumva
umukiriya akeneye nicyo wifuza

313
00:16:57,045 --> 00:16:59,937
(Kirisitiya) nigute cyakwemeza abantu?
nigute inkuru yawe yakwemeza abantu?

314
00:16:59,937 --> 00:17:04,432
(Mariko) Cyane rwose, 
ukeneye kuvuga inkuru nziza kurubuga

315
00:17:04,432 --> 00:17:07,973
Kuberako abantu bazagucira urubanza
bagendeye kuko wabivuze neza

316
00:17:07,973 --> 00:17:11,400
Rero uburyo bakwizera cyangwa wabakurura
nibintu byingenzi cyane

317
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:16,450
Igifite ibi byose
ndimo mvuga hano

318
00:17:16,450 --> 00:17:18,512
Ko ufite kwitegura neza

319
00:17:18,512 --> 00:17:21,294
ukeneye kumva
 ikigaragara neza kubantu bawe

320
00:17:21,294 --> 00:17:25,272
Cyangwa nigute
waba rwiyemezamirimo wizerwa

321
00:17:25,272 --> 00:17:28,301
Ibi ntago ari ingenzi
kubijyanye no kubona amafaranga

322
00:17:28,301 --> 00:17:31,222
Ni ingenzi mubwoko
bwo kubonana nabantu

323
00:17:31,222 --> 00:17:34,538
Ariko hano byumwihariko, kuberako
 abantu bakubona kumbuga gusa

324
00:17:34,538 --> 00:17:36,118
(Kirisitiya)Ibyo nibyo bakubonaho gusa

325
00:17:36,118 --> 00:17:38,164
(Mariko) Cyane rwose, kandi 
urashaka amafaranga muri abo bantu, urabizi?

326
00:17:38,994 --> 00:17:42,851
(Kirisitiya) Rero nkuko mariko yabivuze,
 ibi bintu bifata igihe

327
00:17:42,851 --> 00:17:47,874
Ukeneye gupangira igihe cyawe
gushyiraho icyintu cyemeza abantu

328
00:17:47,874 --> 00:17:50,361
cyizewe, kandi gikurura abantu

329
00:17:51,071 --> 00:17:54,376
Vuga ubutumwa bwawe kandi uvuge
uburambe bwitsinda mukorana

330
00:17:54,376 --> 00:17:56,565
(Mariko) kuberako ibyo bikurura abareba

331
00:17:56,565 --> 00:17:58,991
Bazasakaza ibyo bintu

332
00:17:58,991 --> 00:18:02,657
Bazumva impamvu urimo ubikora
kubera izihe mpamvu urimo kubikora

333
00:18:02,657 --> 00:18:05,284
Ndetse bakumva babyiyumvamo
nkuko umeze

334
00:18:05,284 --> 00:18:06,732
(Kirisitiya) Yego, itegure

335
00:18:06,732 --> 00:18:10,539
Ukeneye gupanga
kandi ukeneye kumenya ibyo wateganya

336
00:18:11,149 --> 00:18:16,440
Bwanyuma, ukeneye gukora ibintu bishoboka
kandi byingenzi bihanze mubihembo

337
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:18,680
Tekereza ibizakurura abantu

338
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:22,758
Niba bari kuguha amafaranga
niki nge nari kuzabaha

339
00:18:22,758 --> 00:18:24,677
Ndetse nigute bazagikunda?

340
00:18:24,677 --> 00:18:26,636
Rero ushobora kuba umuntu uhanga 
kuri ibyo bintu

341
00:18:26,636 --> 00:18:29,362
Kandi ushobora kugurisha ibintu,
 utanga impano

342
00:18:29,362 --> 00:18:31,678
Ugendeye kubintu
byuburyo urimo gukoresha

343
00:18:31,678 --> 00:18:33,066
(Mariko) Kandi wibuke ibyo 
twavuze mukwamamaza

344
00:18:33,066 --> 00:18:35,182
Kuberako ibi, mukwamamaza

345
00:18:35,182 --> 00:18:39,231
Ninko gutakaza ibitekerezo
kurusha amafaranga, muri ubwo buryo

346
00:18:39,231 --> 00:18:41,333
Takaza ibitekerezo
, ubuhanzi, ndetse no kumva

347
00:18:41,333 --> 00:18:46,882
Ese nibihe bihembo runaka
byakurura abantu bazagufasha

348
00:18:46,882 --> 00:18:50,731
(Kirisitiya) kugarura uruziga rwose, 
dutekereza ko gushaka amafaranga

349
00:18:50,731 --> 00:18:54,530
Ari icyintu cyingenzi kuvugaho
kuri ba rwiyemezamirimo uyumunsi

350
00:18:54,530 --> 00:18:56,577
Kandi ninanone
igice cyingenzi cyane muri aya masomo

351
00:18:56,577 --> 00:18:59,339
Kandi wibuke, urimo urateza imbere
gushaka amafaranga kwawe

352
00:18:59,339 --> 00:19:03,105
Muri iri somo, rigufasha kubona amafaranga

353
00:19:03,105 --> 00:19:05,298
Kubona kompanyi yawe wayikuye hasi

354
00:19:05,298 --> 00:19:08,226
Ariko nanone igufasha gutsindira
andi mafaranga y'inyongera

355
00:19:08,226 --> 00:19:12,602
Kuberako dufite amafaranga
yo guha abantu bakoze neza muri iri somo

356
00:19:12,602 --> 00:19:16,258
Amahirwe yo gutsindira amafaranga 
2,500 by'amadolari

357
00:19:16,397 --> 00:19:17,676
Ibyo nibyiza, hoya?

358
00:19:17,676 --> 00:19:20,524
Tugiye kugira
 amashusho iyigisha ryose ritoya

359
00:19:20,524 --> 00:19:24,078
Kuri ibi bintu runaka
kuburyo bwo gukoresha gahunda zitandukanye

360
00:19:24,078 --> 00:19:26,984
Ndetse nuburyo ubona ibijyanye
n'amasomo

361
00:19:26,984 --> 00:19:29,251
Hamwe n'iyamamaza rikura amafaranga muri
rubanda

362
00:19:29,251 --> 00:19:31,661
Tuzakora ibyo mucyumweru cyizaza

363
00:19:32,271 --> 00:19:34,703
Nkakantu karangiza hano, ndatekereza
ibi byaba isomo gusa

364
00:19:34,703 --> 00:19:37,646
Aho ushobora gutsindira amafaranga
uniga icyintu runaka!

365
00:19:37,646 --> 00:19:39,477
Iri niryo somo ryonyine
aho tukwishyura!

366
00:19:39,477 --> 00:19:41,422
(baraseka) cyane rwose.

367
00:19:41,422 --> 00:19:44,776
Rero gumana natwe kandi ukomeze ujye mbere

368
00:19:44,776 --> 00:19:47,085
Icyi nigice kugukura amafaranga
 muri rubanda

369
00:19:47,085 --> 00:19:49,603
Kandi hazaba ibindi bice
kukubona amafaranga bigiye kuza
